Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:16.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:21.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更加爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:43.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的星星让夜色更深沉 梦到的全都是你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:48.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱我 你也装得没有似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:53.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你又在迷恋谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:04.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 男人们啊 心中总是牵挂着无数的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:14.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到处都充满了玫瑰色 我心里实在好烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:25.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:35.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉倒的舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小天 就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我为什么一定要去跑腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来跑腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的筷子盒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他忘记放在书包里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮他送来还赚了一球冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热的天气辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看他根本不需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么 中午还没到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是阿天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚到旁边去 真是倒尽胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恶心透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有几个胃袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要你鸡婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西放在中午就不好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 天气这么热一定会臭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是地球人的食物越看越难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个红色的圆球是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦 这是酸梅 酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好像很难吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你想吃这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想吃这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对难吃的东西还蛮有兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰我吃饭就是这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐 你真是越看越漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天…达令你又对小天做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令每次都一定要作弄小天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有作弄他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么小天会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 立刻住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不服气是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准对女性喷火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要喷火的话 就对我喷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听懂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还蛮有说服力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 站好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这个小鬼喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你对小天做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 你给他灌酒对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒？我不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 对天真无邪的幼童灌酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么恶劣的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该感到羞耻 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始证明我是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是眼镜的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准偷吃 只是借你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准偷吃 我已经算得清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么怀疑我的人格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怀疑才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 我只会拿酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 这里有一颗酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…香肠怎么不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 香肠被你干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 哪有人吃这个就会醉倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是给小天吃酸梅罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在兴奋什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好哭的 可怜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地坐下来看 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群傻瓜 有什么好兴奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 不过是拉姆平常的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 还有没有哪里觉得很热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆 你在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？我才没有醉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了 吃酸梅竟然会醉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦 我没有醉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把酸梅交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把酸梅交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 拉姆小姐还真难伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个家伙也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当里多放几颗酸梅不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 卷发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天的便当是三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没有酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂这样下去行吗 你有酸梅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我今天的午餐是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭团加法国料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让拉姆小姐吃酸梅吃个痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是鱼子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个包鱼肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳酪 果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田蜗肉 比目鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莺馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我反对法国厨师煮日本菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有酸梅吗 赶快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了 再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你是副班长赶快想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们难道不会自己想办法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一开溜她一定会追过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最糟糕的酒品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾不能再为各位效力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太烂了 这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将计就计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿当 看看你干得好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐醉醺醺地跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把她弄醉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？他比拉姆更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 你去阻止小天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比拉姆小姐更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就交给你处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快去找拉姆小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得陪我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是这么倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快把她找出来就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不是达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 拉姆小姐 回教室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子赶快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼…不 跑去找小天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 跟我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 达令竟然认为小天比我还重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 怎么你也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让拉姆姐一个人霸占酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我为什么会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天也喜欢吃酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太喜欢了 太棒了 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 把达令一起叫过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令竟然认为小天比我更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是对小天移情别恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟然敢对达令横刀夺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不稀罕那个呆子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 你说我的达令是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令哪一点是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正阿当就是个呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅？酸梅到底怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 已经没有时间说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因相当的复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再问了快让我们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽快的争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个顽固的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拼命阻止被害人数的增加\N你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一瞬间也许因为你的妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的破坏电流又在校内徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的话快让我们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有弄清楚绝对不让你们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为再继续吃酸梅 拉姆就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要挡在走道的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 叫你不要挡路听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉 拉姆小姐 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小天等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 全部给我进教室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始检查携带物品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查携带物品？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要耍我 一定有人带酒来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个紧要关头还跑来找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 不能再拖拖拉拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:17:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这可是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找不到酒的话你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要公开道歉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我找到酒的话 你们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讲找不到你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 被我找出来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我就跳脱衣舞给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱衣舞…就这么说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士不二言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼天 小鬼天 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走快一点 这都是你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑的这么辛苦 你还那么悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必这么傻呢 去吃碗拉面如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了这么久还没找到 一定是跑校外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去吃拉面吧 拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉的人是没有办法下定义的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烧伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蛮清楚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是第三十八个了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那个鬼丫头真是难伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花小姐有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 突然冲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地赶来救你 不应该这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么又突然冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花 用这个治疗一下伤口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用酒喷伤口可以治疗烫伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然拿着酒四处闲逛 破戒僧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口对口治疗吧
