Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒 酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 太好了 酒 酒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照约定吧 给我跳脱衣舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照约定 还是请你跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 连你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你跟他约定的 男人就要负责
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你脱衣舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你们竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是多灾多难
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这么热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
